column10: a must have for any call, animaze has customizable options for models that let you edit shapes and colors, plus you can add leapmotion tracker and mocap hands with most of the avatars.

Don't waste your money on this app like I did. The avatars are just no no. Even when you are just moving your head without mic, your mouth opens as if you are talking. Try other apps if you really want something worth your money.
